{"tid":1913521,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"黎明根本就係黃絲，不服來辯","createTime":"2020-03-07T00:34:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-07T10:51:48.000Z","uid":213877,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"9c5764cc700999a5d70845758268f836e1bc7b82","tid":1913521,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T00:34:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://obs.line-scdn.net/0hdTO1_JKMO3tySBN-FctELEgeOBRBJCh4Fn5qZC0mZU8Lf38qHntxTl5AbUxafXwlHH5xH1FPIEoMcCglTnxx/w644\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fobs.line-scdn.net%2F0hdTO1_JKMO3tySBN-FctELEgeOBRBJCh4Fn5qZC0mZU8Lf38qHntxTl5AbUxafXwlHH5xH1FPIEoMcCglTnxx%2Fw644&h=632a426e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎疫情令不少藝人出騷機會大減，寰亞音樂旗下 17 組藝人歌手此時一齊拍攝打氣影片「齊抗疫  香港地」，鼓勵市民以積極心態面對疫情。影片以歌曲《香港地》作為背景音樂，黎明、楊千嬅、草蜢、王菀之等藝人在片中分享抗疫知識，例如外出戴口罩、避免到人多聚集地方、多休息、勤洗手等。<br />\n寰亞音樂今日上載一條3分鐘長的影片，以「齊抗疫  香港地」為主題，片中共有 17 組寰亞藝人登場，包括黎明、楊千嬅、草蜢(蔡一智、蘇志威、蔡一傑)、王菀之、梁漢文、SoulJase、梁釗峰、陳健安、馮允謙、林曉峰、黎曉陽、蘇麗珊、鄧小巧、NowhereBoys、黃淑蔓等。<br />\n不過這條為香港人打氣的影片，惹來網民部分批評聲音，例如不滿片中梁漢文以「新型冠狀病毒」代替「武漢肺炎」，亦有人提出，楊千嬅過去曾高調親中，曾公開表示一心擁護基本法，「香港是中國不可分割的一部分」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唱一首歌可以代表到咩 ？黎明 ？黃絲黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b704667c1759f3e806ee93e608a14b80967434ad","tid":1913521,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T00:35:28.000Z","msg":"黎明係黃絲，不服來瓣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://today.line.me/hk/pc/article/寰亞眾星拍防疫打氣片%E3%80%80黎明楊千嬅牽頭+17+藝人為港人打氣︰齊齊抗疫%E3%80%80你做得到-N2EPB1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftoday.line.me%2Fhk%2Fpc%2Farticle%2F%E5%AF%B0%E4%BA%9E%E7%9C%BE%E6%98%9F%E6%8B%8D%E9%98%B2%E7%96%AB%E6%89%93%E6%B0%